\f1\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 13\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For he has rescued us from the dominion of darkness\'a0and brought us into the kingdom of the Son he loves,\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can we just admit there is this darkness that is present at times\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I think after a week like this week we\'92re probably all a little more open to saying there are things that are evil and that there is this dominion of darkness\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Whether you believe in God you probably have said things like \'93that is just wrong or evil or terrible\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf0 As a culture we just go back and forth dealing with the symptoms and throwing whatever we think of to help the situation and so we:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Discipline people\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Love people \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Educate people\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Age of Enlightenment\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Then world war 1 and 2 came\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
Until we deal with the real issues then we are putting band aid on our cancer.\
\
I\'92m going to cheat ahead a little bit and go to one of my go to verses in life\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 20\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Since you died with Christ\'a0to the elemental spiritual forces of this world,\'a0why, as though you still belonged to the world, do you submit to its rules:\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 21\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Do not handle! Do not taste! Do not touch!\'94?\'a0 
\f4\b\fs18 \super 22\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub These rules, which have to do with things that are all destined to perish with use, are based on merely human commands and teachings.\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 23\'a0
\f5\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Such regulations indeed have an appearance of wisdom, with their self-imposed worship, their false humility\'a0and their harsh treatment of the body, but they lack any value in restraining sensual indulgence.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f2 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I want to be really clear that all those things are good things.  I\'92m not trying to say that the spiritual person rejects counseling and coaching and discipline and doesn\'92t need people to love them\'85It\'92s not just them and Jesus and they\'92ll figure it out alone\'85that is not the Gospel and not the purpose of the church.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What I am saying is that as long as we keep thinking the problem isn\'92t spiritual and deeper than our self-help issues then we will continue to struggle in a world we can\'92t make sense of.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why it is SO important to understand this section of scripture today\'85because as a church we are called to be different and deal with issues differently\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf4 Transition:  And so the first thing Paul says here is that we have been rescued!\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here\'92s what that doesn\'92t mean\'85it doesn\'92t mean:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bad things don\'92t happen to you any more\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You don\'92t struggle with things anymore\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What it does mean is if you are a Christian then this is not a subtle lifestyle change but a dramatically new kingdom with which you live in and in turn a different king to live by.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Peter says the same thing a little differently about us being rescued and what that means for us\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 11\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Dear friends,\'a0I urge you, as foreigners and exiles,\'a0to abstain from sinful desires,\'a0which wage war against your soul.\'a0  1 Peter 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question: Are you light to this world or do you just blend in?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We have been rescued to show the world there is a different way to live life.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}WE ARE THE SOLUTION TO THE PROBLEM OF EVIL!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf2 \super 14\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub in whom we have redemption,\'a0the forgiveness of sins.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}QUESTION:  Do you believe in sin?  Really?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The biggest problem we have in our culture today is not the darkness!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf6 Illustration of the people asking why the darkness is so dark instead of asking why the light isn\'92t bright brighter?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs18 \cf2 \super 15\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The Son is the image\'a0of the invisible God,\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you want to know what God looks like and how He acts read the Gospels!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 the firstborn\'a0over all creation.\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 16\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For in him all things were created:\'a0things in heaven and on earth, visible and invisible, whether thrones or powers or rulers or authorities;\'a0all things have been created through him and for him.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs18 \cf2 \super 17\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He is before all things,\'a0and in him all things hold together.\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 18\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And he is the head\'a0of the body, the church;\'a0\
\
\
he is the beginning and the firstborn\'a0from among the dead,\'a0\
\
\
so that in everything he might have the supremacy.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Paul is making a case that Jesus is Lord and therefore has the power to do anything He wants.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He goes on\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 19\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For God was pleased\'a0to have all his fullness dwell in him,\'a0
\f4\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and through him to reconcile\'a0to himself all things, whether things on earth or things in heaven,\'a0\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reason Jesus needs to reconcile things is because they are broken.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Until we understand the solution is Jesus\'85not ANYTHING ELSE\'85we will fail in our attempts to right this world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The answer is Jesus, the solution is Jesus, the one who can reconcile everything is Jesus.\
